{"id":20,"date":"2022-02-08T09:58:40","date_gmt":"2022-02-08T06:58:40","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.drbasarerdogan.com\/?p=20"},"modified":"2022-02-08T11:21:06","modified_gmt":"2022-02-08T08:21:06","slug":"botoks","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.drbasarerdogan.com\/botoks\/","title":{"rendered":"Botoks"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Botoks (Botulinum toksini), Clostridium botulinum adl\u0131 bakteriden elde edilen bir \u00e7e\u015fit toksindir.<\/p>\n<p>Sinir iletiminin durmas\u0131, sinirin ula\u015ft\u0131\u011f\u0131 organ\u0131n i\u015flevlerinin azalmas\u0131n\u0131 ya da tamamen kaybolmas\u0131n\u0131 sa\u011flar. Bu sayede de kaslara iletim gidemez.Klinik kullan\u0131m\u0131 i\u00e7in laboratuar ortam\u0131nda da \u00fcretilebilinen Botoks uzun y\u0131llar medikal estetik t\u0131p alan\u0131nda de\u011fi\u015fik hastal\u0131klarda kullan\u0131lm\u0131\u015f olup g\u00fcn\u00fcm\u00fczde estetik ama\u00e7l\u0131 uygulamalar s\u0131n\u0131f\u0131nda olduk\u00e7a pop\u00fcler hale gelmi\u015ftir. Belki de Botoks g\u00fcn\u00fcm\u00fcz\u00fcn en yayg\u0131n estetik uygulamas\u0131d\u0131r. Botoks&#8217;un etki mekanizmas\u0131ndan t\u0131pta bir\u00e7ok alanda yararlan\u0131lmaktad\u0131r.<\/p>\n<p>Y\u00fczdeki mimik kaslar\u0131n\u0131n y\u0131llarca istemsiz olarak kas\u0131lmas\u0131 neticesinde deri \u00fczerinde \u00e7izgiler ve k\u0131r\u0131\u015f\u0131kl\u0131klar meydana gelir.Bu nedenle genellikle mimik kaslar\u0131n\u0131n kas\u0131lmas\u0131 ile olu\u015fan y\u00fcz ve boyun b\u00f6lgesindeki k\u0131r\u0131\u015f\u0131kl\u0131k ve \u00e7izgilenmeleri azaltmak m\u00fcmk\u00fcnken ayn\u0131 zamanda \u00a0migren a\u011fr\u0131lar\u0131 tedavisinde ve a\u015f\u0131r\u0131 terleyen b\u00f6lgelerdeki terlemeyi azaltmak amac\u0131 ile kullan\u0131l\u0131r.<\/p>\n<p><strong>\u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>Botox&#8217;un En S\u0131k Kullan\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131 Mimik \u00c7izgileri<\/strong><strong><br \/>\n<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Al\u0131n, ka\u015f aras\u0131, kaz ayaklar\u0131, \u00a0g\u00f6z \u00e7evresi ve alt\u0131, dudak \u00fcst\u00fc, boyun platizma bantlar\u0131 ve a\u011f\u0131z \u00e7evresinde g\u00f6r\u00fcl\u00fcr. Bu \u00e7izgiler ki\u015fiye daha ya\u015fl\u0131 bir g\u00f6r\u00fcn\u00fcm, ka\u015flar aras\u0131ndaki \u00e7izgiler ise ki\u015fiye \u00e7at\u0131k ka\u015fl\u0131, k\u0131zg\u0131n ve sinirli bir bak\u0131\u015f ifadesi verir.<\/p>\n<p>Botoks uygulanarak mimic kaslar\u0131n\u0131n hareketleri zay\u0131flat\u0131l\u0131r, kas hareketlerindeki azalma, \u00fczerindeki derinin, kas hareketleri ile katlanmas\u0131n\u0131 ve katlanmaya ba\u011fl\u0131 \u00e7izgilenmeyi de azalt\u0131r.<\/p>\n<p>Bu \u015fekilde ya\u015fl\u0131,k\u0131zg\u0131n,sinirli,yorgun \u00a0olarak g\u00f6r\u00fcnen y\u00fcz ifadesinde de belirgin bir d\u00fczelme sa\u011flan\u0131r.<\/p>\n<p><strong>\u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>Botoks&#8217;un Etkisi Ne Zaman Ba\u015flar, Ne Kadar S\u00fcrer?<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Botoks uygulamas\u0131 yap\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131nda etki 2-3 g\u00fcn sonra ba\u015flar, 14-15 g\u00fcn sonra tam rand\u0131manl\u0131 hale gelir. Bu d\u00f6nemden sonra etkide art\u0131\u015f fazla g\u00f6zlenmez, 3-4 aydan itibaren Botoks&#8217;un etkisi azalmaya ba\u015flar ve 6 ay\u0131n sonunda 1 y\u0131l aras\u0131nda tamamen biter.<\/p>\n<p><strong>\u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>Botoks <\/strong><strong>Kullan\u0131m Alanlar\u0131<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>Al\u0131n <\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Al\u0131n b\u00f6lgemizde ka\u015flar\u0131n kald\u0131r\u0131lmas\u0131 ile olu\u015fan mimik \u00e7izgi ve hareketlerimize ba\u011fl\u0131 genellikle yatay olan \u00e7izgilerdir. Al\u0131n b\u00f6lgesine yap\u0131lan al\u0131n Botoks ile bu yatay ve bazen dikey \u00e7izgilerden kurtulmak m\u00fcmk\u00fcn olmaktad\u0131r.<\/p>\n<p><strong>\u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>Ka\u015f Aras\u0131 <\/strong><\/p>\n<p>G\u00f6zlerimizi odaklad\u0131\u011f\u0131m\u0131z zaman ya da k\u0131zg\u0131n oldu\u011fumuz zaman ka\u015flar\u0131n \u00e7at\u0131lmas\u0131 ile olu\u015fan iki ka\u015f aras\u0131ndaki dikey \u00e7izgilerdir.\u00e7ok fazla belirgin olan iki ka\u015f aras\u0131 b\u00f6lgede olu\u015fan k\u0131r\u0131\u015f\u0131kl\u0131klard\u0131r.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><strong>G\u00f6z \u00c7evresi &#8211; Kaz Ayaklar\u0131 <\/strong><\/p>\n<p>\u0130nsanlar g\u00fcld\u00fckleri zaman g\u00f6z \u00e7evreleri de buna e\u015flik eder ve buna ba\u011fl\u0131 g\u00f6z kenar\u0131nda ve alt\u0131nda k\u0131r\u0131\u015f\u0131kl\u0131klar olu\u015fur. Botoks uygulamas\u0131 bu alandaki k\u0131r\u0131\u015f\u0131kl\u0131klar\u0131 b\u00fcy\u00fck \u00f6l\u00e7\u00fcde azaltmaktad\u0131r.<\/p>\n<p><strong>\u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>Dudak \u00dcst\u00fc <\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Dudak \u00fcst\u00fcnde bulunan genellikle sigara i\u00e7imine ba\u011fl\u0131 ince dikey k\u0131r\u0131\u015f\u0131kl\u0131klar\u0131 d\u00fczeltmede botoks \u00e7ok etkilidir. Yine dudak k\u00f6\u015felerini a\u015fa\u011f\u0131ya \u00e7eken kaslara da botoks yap\u0131labilmektedir. Bu durumda dudak k\u00f6\u015feleri bir miktar yukar\u0131ya do\u011fru d\u00f6ner ve mutsuz ifade yerini daha gen\u00e7 g\u00f6r\u00fcn\u00fcme b\u0131rak\u0131r.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><strong>\u00c7ene <\/strong><\/p>\n<p>\u00c7ene u\u00e7lar\u0131nda g\u00fcl\u00fcnce ya da konu\u015funca olu\u015fan k\u0131r\u0131\u015f\u0131kl\u0131klara botoks uygulanabilir.<\/p>\n<p><strong>\u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>Burun <\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Botoks&#8217;un bir di\u011fer kullan\u0131m alan\u0131 burun ucunu kald\u0131rmaya y\u00f6neliktir. Baz\u0131 burunlarda burun ucu konu\u015furken ve g\u00fclerken a\u015fa\u011f\u0131ya do\u011fru sarkar ve yer de\u011fi\u015ftirir. Bunu yapan burun ile \u00fcst dudak aras\u0131nda bir akordeon gibi kas\u0131lan M.Depressor Septi kas\u0131d\u0131r.<\/p>\n<p>Burnun alt k\u0131s\u0131mlar\u0131na yap\u0131lan botoksla burun u\u00e7 k\u0131sm\u0131 bir miktar kalkmakt